      <title>manim_1</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/25/manim-1/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/25/manim-1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是在做一个和极坐标相关的题目时写出来的一个动画</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> manim <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">LogScalingExample</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">Scene</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">construct</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 定义极坐标函数 r(theta) = cos(theta) + sin(theta)</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">polar_function</span>(<span class="params">theta</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            r = np.cos(theta) + np.sin(theta)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> r * np.array([np.cos(theta), np.sin(theta), <span class="number">0</span>])  <span class="comment"># 返回笛卡尔坐标系中的点</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 创建曲线</span></span><br><span class="line">        curve = ParametricFunction(</span><br><span class="line">            polar_function,</span><br><span class="line">            t_range=[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span> * np.pi],  <span class="comment"># theta 的范围</span></span><br><span class="line">            color=BLUE,</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 创建方格，直角坐标系的交点默认为原点，只要不指定x轴,y轴的范围</span></span><br><span class="line">        grid = NumberPlane(</span><br><span class="line">            axis_config=&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;include_numbers&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">True</span>,  <span class="comment"># 显示坐标轴上的数字</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;stroke_color&quot;</span>: WHITE,  <span class="comment"># 坐标轴颜色为白色</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;include_tip&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">True</span>  <span class="comment"># 添加箭头</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">          )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 画出方格背景</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.play(Create(grid))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 原点</span></span><br><span class="line">        origin = Dot(color=RED)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 原点添加标签</span></span><br><span class="line">        label_o = MathTex(<span class="string">&quot;o&quot;</span>).add_updater(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> m: m.next_to(origin,DOWN))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.add(origin,label_o)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 使用ValueTracker跟踪角度theta</span></span><br><span class="line">        theta_tracker = ValueTracker(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 点P（黄色点），位置随theta变化</span></span><br><span class="line">        p_dot = Dot(color=YELLOW)</span><br><span class="line">        p_dot.add_updater(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> m: m.move_to(polar_function(theta_tracker.get_value())))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># P点添加标签</span></span><br><span class="line">        label_p = MathTex(<span class="string">&quot;p&quot;</span>).add_updater(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> m: m.next_to(p_dot, UP))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.add(p_dot,label_p)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment"># 实时更新的OP线段（绿色）</span></span><br><span class="line">        op_line = always_redraw(<span class="keyword">lambda</span>: Line(origin.get_center(), p_dot.get_center(), color=GREEN))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.add(op_line)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 作出图像</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.play(Create(curve))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment"># 运行动画：让theta在4秒内从0变化到2π</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.play(</span><br><span class="line">            theta_tracker.animate.set_value(<span class="number">2</span> * PI),</span><br><span class="line">            run_time=<span class="number">4</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            rate_func=linear</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.wait()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div style="position: relative; padding: 30% 0; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">  <iframe     src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114065036804408&bvid=BV1npPieBEst&cid=28575468836&p=1"     style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;"     scrolling="no"     frameborder="no"     framespacing="0"     allowfullscreen="true">  </iframe></div>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 学习 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> manim </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>git端口22超时连接</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/02/git%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A322%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/02/git%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A322%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用<code>git push</code>出现以下错误</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh: connect to host github.com port 22: Connection timed out</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解决方法</p><p>在<code>C:\Users\用户名\.ssh</code>目录下新建<code>config</code>文件，用记事本打开该文件，粘贴以下内容</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Host github.com</span><br><span class="line">  Hostname ssh.github.com</span><br><span class="line">  Port 443</span><br><span class="line">  User git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>粘贴以下命令到命令行进行验证</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后应该会出现三个选项其中有yes&#x2F;no&#x2F;还有一个忘掉了，输入yes就可以了。成功后会出现以下内容</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hi username! You<span class="string">&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上后半句话不影响我们使用git的相关操作， 只是不提供登录服务器的 Shell 终端权限。<br>例如：你无法通过ssh <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#x68;&#117;&#98;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#109;">git@github.com</a> 登录到 GitHub 的服务器上执行 ls、cd 等命令。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> questions </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Termux 教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/01/29/Termux-%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/01/29/Termux-%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Termux的图形化界面"><a href="#Termux的图形化界面" class="headerlink" title="Termux的图形化界面"></a>Termux的图形化界面</h2><p>这里推荐github上的一个termux图形化界面的项目。</p><p>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/LinuxDroidMaster/Termux-Desktops">https://github.com/LinuxDroidMaster/Termux-Desktops</a></p><p>这个项目使用三种方式安装图形化界面：</p><ul><li><p>termux的本地环境</p></li><li><p>proot环境</p></li><li><p>chroot环境（需要root）</p></li></ul><p>本文只介绍前两种安装方式, 使用的图形化界面软件是Termux: X11</p><h3 id="termux本地安装图形化界面"><a href="#termux本地安装图形化界面" class="headerlink" title="termux本地安装图形化界面"></a>termux本地安装图形化界面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg update</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install x11-repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install termux-x11-nightly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install pulseaudio  // 可以在图形界面中播放音频</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装xfce, xfce是一个轻量级的桌面环境。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install xfce4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你想要安装火狐浏览器：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install tur-repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install firefox</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你想要安装vscode：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install tur-repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install code-oss</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从github仓库中下载桌面环境启动脚本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install wget</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LinuxDroidMaster/Termux-Desktops/main/scripts/termux_native/startxfce4_termux.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动桌面环境</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> +x startxfce4_termux.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./startxfce4_termux.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="proot环境安装图形化界面"><a href="#proot环境安装图形化界面" class="headerlink" title="proot环境安装图形化界面"></a>proot环境安装图形化界面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg update</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install x11-repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install termux-x11-nightly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install pulseaudio  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里以debian为例, 安装debian</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install proot-distro</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">proot-distro install debian</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">proot-distro login debian</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装sudo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">apt update &amp;&amp; apt install -y <span class="built_in">sudo</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置中国上海时区</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> <span class="built_in">ln</span> -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在proot环境中设置普通用户, 这里用户名设置为droidmaster（因为启动图形化界面的bash脚本中的用户名是droidmaster）。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">useradd -m droidmaster</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">passwd droidmaster // 用户设置密码, 密码输入时不可见</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将用户加入 sudo 组</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">usermod -aG <span class="built_in">sudo</span> droidmaster</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将droidmaster添加到用户列表</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">apt install vim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/sudoers</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在打开文件的末尾添加以下内容, 保存文件并退出</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">droidmaster ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换到用户</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">su - droidmaster</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装xfce</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install xfce4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>退出proot环境, 安装启动脚本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LinuxDroidMaster/Termux-Desktops/main/scripts/proot_debian/startxfce4_debian.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动桌面环境</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> +x startxfce4_debian.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./startxfce4_debian.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关于图形界面其它的安装方式, 可以到github上去查看。</p><h2 id="Termux主题美化"><a href="#Termux主题美化" class="headerlink" title="Termux主题美化"></a>Termux主题美化</h2><h3 id="Termux更改字体"><a href="#Termux更改字体" class="headerlink" title="Termux更改字体"></a>Termux更改字体</h3><p>从<a href="https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93">https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads下载字体</a>, 这里以0xProtoNerdFont-Regular.ttf字体为例。</p><p>创建字体文件夹</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p ~/.termux/fonts</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在home目录下将字体0xProtoNerdFont-Regular.ttf复制一份到fonts文件夹下。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> 0xProtoNerdFont-Regular.ttf ~/.termux/fonts</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将0xProtoNerdFont-Regular.ttf移动到.termux目录下的font.ttf文件中。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> 0xProtoNerdFont-Regular.ttf ~/.termux/font.ttf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启termux, 使用以下命令测试nerd字体是否应用到termux中, 如果输出了图标说明nerd安装成功</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="string">&quot;\ue0b0 \u26a1 \ue709&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Termux安装Oh-my-zsh"><a href="#Termux安装Oh-my-zsh" class="headerlink" title="Termux安装Oh my zsh"></a>Termux安装Oh my zsh</h3><p><strong>Oh My Zsh 是基于 Zsh Shell 的配置框架</strong>, 它本身并不是一个独立的 Shell, 而是对 Zsh 的增强和扩展。</p><p>安装zsh, 并设置为默认终端, 重启termux。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pkg install zsh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chsh -s zsh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将.bashrc中的内容复制到.zshrc文件当中</p><p>安装Oh My Zsh</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$(wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 国内用户可使用以下命令</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$(wget -O- https://install.ohmyz.sh)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置-powerlevel10k-主题"><a href="#配置-powerlevel10k-主题" class="headerlink" title="配置 powerlevel10k 主题"></a>配置 powerlevel10k 主题</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> --depth=1 https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k.git <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/themes/powerlevel10k&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 国内用户可使用以下命令</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> --depth=1 https://gitee.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k.git <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/themes/powerlevel10k&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑~&#x2F;.zshrc文件, 将<code>ZSH_THEME</code>设置为<code>&quot;powerlevel10k/powerlevel10k&quot;</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ZSH_THEME = <span class="string">&quot;powerlevel10k/powerlevel10k&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="插件安装"><a href="#插件安装" class="headerlink" title="插件安装"></a>插件安装</h3><h4 id="zsh-autosuggestions"><a href="#zsh-autosuggestions" class="headerlink" title="zsh-autosuggestions"></a>zsh-autosuggestions</h4><p>zsh-autosuggestions是能够自动补全命令的插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions <span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑.zshrc文件, 在 <code>plugin</code> 中添加 <code>zsh-autosuggestions</code>, 重启termux。</p><p>插件之间以空格分开</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plugins=(</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="zsh-syntax-highlighting"><a href="#zsh-syntax-highlighting" class="headerlink" title="zsh-syntax-highlighting"></a>zsh-syntax-highlighting</h4><p>zsh-syntax-highlighting是能够判断命令是否正确的插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git <span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑.zshrc文件, 在 <code>plugin</code> 中添加 <code>zsh-syntax-highlighting</code>, 重启termux。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plugins=(</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Termux安装各种包"><a href="#Termux安装各种包" class="headerlink" title="Termux安装各种包"></a>Termux安装各种包</h2><h3 id="manim"><a href="#manim" class="headerlink" title="manim"></a>manim</h3><p>Manim 是一个基于 Python 的动画引擎，用于高效制作数学演示和可视化动画。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install cmake</span><br><span class="line">pkg install tur-repo</span><br><span class="line">pkg install manim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果以上方法不行的话，可以试试下面的方法，先安装ubuntu，再安装manim<br><a href="https://youtu.be/fGC6RNdvBXA">原视频链接</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg update &amp;&amp; pkg upgrade -y &amp;&amp; pkg install wget proot git -y &amp;&amp; \</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~ &amp;&amp; git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/MFDGaming/ubuntu-in-termux &amp;&amp; \</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ubuntu-in-termux &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">chmod</span> +x ubuntu.sh &amp;&amp; ./ubuntu.sh -y &amp;&amp; ./startubuntu.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get update </span><br><span class="line">apt-get upgrade </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">apt-get install <span class="built_in">sudo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt update </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install build-essential python3-dev libcairo2-dev libpango1.0-dev ffmpeg </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// texlive可以选择不安装</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install texlive</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install texlive-latex-extra</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install python3-pip </span><br><span class="line">apt install python3.12-venv</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 更推荐使用pipx安装manim，因为不需要激活虚拟环境</span><br><span class="line">apt install install pipx</span><br><span class="line">pipx install manim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假设你的文件名是main.py，生成动画的命令：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">manim --resolution <span class="number">2560</span>,<span class="number">1440</span> main.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将分辨率设置为2k及以上才能保证所有的动画都只在视频内，如果不能的话，将 <code>--resolution 2560,1440</code>替换为<code>-qk</code>。</p><h3 id="安装mpv"><a href="#安装mpv" class="headerlink" title="安装mpv"></a>安装mpv</h3><p>mpv是一个命令行音乐播放器</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install mpv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还要安装 <code>pulseaudio</code>和 <code>ffmpeg</code>，才能在命令行中播放音乐。<br><code>pkg install pulseaudio ffmpeg</code></p><p>播放音乐</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pulseaudio --start</span><br><span class="line">mpv --ao=pulse your_audio_file.mp3 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果要停止音乐</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkill mpv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装cava"><a href="#安装cava" class="headerlink" title="安装cava"></a>安装cava</h3><p>但是在终端中播放音乐有些单调，可以安装 <code>cava</code>音频可视化工具<br><code>pkg install cava</code></p><p>播放音乐时同时显示音频</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pulseaudio --start</span><br><span class="line">mpv --ao=pulse your_audio_file.mp3 &amp; cava</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下图所示<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aric6494/images/main/img/1738379894565.jpg"></p><p>cava的配置文件在 <code>.config/cava/config</code>，可以编辑配置文件自定义音频可视化时的颜色。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
